net.proteusframework.ui.search

Interface PropertyConstraint

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Cloneable, SearchConstraint
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractPropertyConstraint, ComboBoxConstraint, DateConstraint, FixedSearchConstraint, SimpleConstraint

    public interface PropertyConstraint
extends SearchConstraint
    Represents a search constraint that is tied to a property on an entity or a column in a database table.
    Author:
    Russ Tennant (russ@i2rd.com)

        Defaults to true.
